messages.content: I'm calling from the Sheraton, Baltimore North.
We have a dead body in one of our rooms.
Okay, I can help you. Let me take some information so we can send help out there. What's the address?
The address is 903 Dulaney Valley Road.
Okay, 903 Dulaney Valley Road off Fairman Avenue. What room number?
And the phone number you're calling from?
I'm calling from my cell phone.
Okay. Do you know if it's a male or a female?
Any idea how this might have happened?
I don't know. I'm not going further into the room than what I just saw at the entrance.

Okay. Just letting you know, we have already sent a call for police, fire, and ambulance to be on the way. If you find any more information, give us a call back. If you don't want to go in the room, definitely don't. Help will be there as soon as they can.
